    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>チェスター</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Chester</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>エターナルソードを
あなた達に渡すわけにはいきません</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I can't hand the Eternal Sword over to you.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>どうして！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why not?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……ごめんなさい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...I'm sorry.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>謝られてもわからないよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You apologizing won't help me understand!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>責めないであげてよ。
リアラが悪いわけじゃないんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Don't fault her for this.
Reala's not the one to blame here.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>渡さないって言われて
はいそうですかって納得できるわけあるか！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>How are we supposed to just say,
"okay, that's alright", when she says that to us?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>オレ達にはエターナルソードの力が
必要なんだ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We need the Eternal Sword's power!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>それが目の前にあるのに
諦められるわけねぇだろう！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The thing's right in front of us! We're not giving up!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>僕もチェスターと同じ意見だ。
ここまで来て
諦めて帰る事なんてできない！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>My feelings are the same as Chester's.
We can't give up and go home after
we've made it this far!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>来るの！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Are you gonna fight us over it?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>仕方ないわ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So there's nothing else to be done about it...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
